author: jplevyak
msg: Fix 2 gcc 4.5 compilation issues. INKHttpStatus, in addition to having
strange capitalization doesn't have a error code and so uses
INK_ERROR which is a different enum.  gcc 4.5 is strict about such things.
This should really be fixed, but this patch at least cleans up the compile.

msg: Fix pool parameter order on svn_wc_upgrade_get_repos_info_t. Some minor
(ensure_repos_info): ... this. we only want to ensure the repos info is
